Hello!!!

Well, this is my Official First MAP!!! (I said official, because I had another that it was a kind of GunGame when I was fooling around with the Hammer Editor).

Ok, let's go talk about this particular map. I had used it in my clan server, and we found that there is no supremacy for one type of weapon to another, and is a kind of map that a camper doesn't have too much advantage.

About the map:
1- A night environment
2- two spawn CT base
3- two spawn T  base
4- 6 hostages
5- two rescue areas
6- Total number of players: 24 (12x12)
7- Map size: MEDIUM
